{"metadata":{"externalID":"s:10NordicMesh14LightHSLHueSetV5delays5UInt8VSgvp","roleHeading":"Instance Property","symbolKind":"property","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"let"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"delay"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"UInt8","preciseIdentifier":"s:s5UInt8V"},{"kind":"text","text":"?"}],"title":"delay","modules":[{"name":"NordicMesh"}]},"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh","doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/LightHSLHueSet"]]},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/LightHSLHueSet\/delay","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Message execution delay in 5 millisecond steps."}],"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"let"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"delay"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"UInt8","preciseIdentifier":"s:s5UInt8V"},{"kind":"text","text":"?"}],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","level":2,"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The purpose of this field is to synchronize transitions initiated"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"by sending the same message multiple times with a short delay."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"For example, a Node would want to send a Generic On Off Set"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Unacknowledged message to a Group Address. In order to increase"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"changes of successful delivery, such message can be repeated."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The first message could be sent with longer "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/TransitionMessage\/delay"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and each following with a shorter one, so when different Nodes"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"receive different messages, the action they take seems more"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"synchronized."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This file has to be set together with "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/TransitionMessage\/transitionTime","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"."}]}]}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/nordicmesh\/lighthslhueset\/delay"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"references":{"doc://NordicMesh/documentation/NordicMesh/TransitionMessage/delay":{"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/TransitionMessage\/delay","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/nordicmesh\/transitionmessage\/delay","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Message execution delay in 5 millisecond steps."}],"required":true,"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"delay","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"UInt8","preciseIdentifier":"s:s5UInt8V","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":"?","kind":"text"}],"title":"delay"},"doc://NordicMesh/documentation/NordicMesh/TransitionMessage/transitionTime":{"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/TransitionMessage\/transitionTime","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/nordicmesh\/transitionmessage\/transitiontime","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The Transition Time field identifies the time that an Element will"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"take to transition to the target state from the present state."}],"required":true,"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"transitionTime"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"TransitionTime","preciseIdentifier":"s:10NordicMesh14TransitionTimeV"},{"kind":"text","text":"?"}],"title":"transitionTime"},"doc://NordicMesh/documentation/NordicMesh/LightHSLHueSet":{"role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/nordicmesh\/lighthslhueset","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"LightHSLHueSet","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/LightHSLHueSet","title":"LightHSLHueSet","fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"LightHSLHueSet","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","abstract":[]},"doc://NordicMesh/documentation/NordicMesh/LightHSLHueSet/delay":{"fragments":[{"text":"let","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"delay","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"UInt8","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:s5UInt8V"},{"text":"?","kind":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/LightHSLHueSet\/delay","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/nordicmesh\/lighthslhueset\/delay","title":"delay","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Message execution delay in 5 millisecond steps."}],"role":"symbol"},"doc://NordicMesh/documentation/NordicMesh":{"abstract":[{"text":"Provision, configure and control Bluetooth mesh devices with nRF Mesh library.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","role":"collection","title":"NordicMesh","url":"\/documentation\/nordicmesh","identifier":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh"}}}